{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"ccnvwOzdD1i7"},"source":["## Gunting Batu Kertas\n","Permainan sederhana antara dua pemain. Masing-masing memilih salah satu dari:\n","- Gunting\n","- Batu\n","- Kertas\n","\n","&nbsp;\n","#### **Logika Permainan:**\n","- Gunting menang lawan Kertas\n","- Kertas menang lawan Batu\n","- Batu menang lawan Gunting\n","- Jika pilihan sama, maka Seri\n","\n","&nbsp;\n","#### **Kebutuhan Sistem:**\n","- Input:\n","    - Pemain memasukkan pilihan: \"batu\", \"gunting\", atau \"kertas\"\n","    - Komputer memilih secara acak dari pilihan yang sama\n","- Validasi Input:\n","    - Program hanya menerima input yang termasuk dalam `[\"batu\", \"gunting\", \"kertas\"]`\n","    - Jika tidak valid, tampilkan pesan kesalahan\n","    - Penanganan Case Sensitif\n","- Output:\n","    - Tampilkan pilihan pemain dan komputer\n","    - Tampilkan hasil permainan\n","- Looping Permainan:\n","    - Setelah 1 ronde, pemain diberi pilihan untuk main lagi\n","    - Jika memilih selain \"y\", permainan berhenti dan tampilkan pesan penutup\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["import random\n","\n","random.choice(['batu', 'gunting', 'kertas'])"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":35},"id":"tNCWYJuNscdt","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1744624051813,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":6,"user":{"displayName":"Elmo Allistair","userId":"10987414782066235031"}},"outputId":"cc0ee0d4-c134-491a-cd49-ea1e5c434695"},"execution_count":11,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["'batu'"],"application/vnd.google.colaboratory.intrinsic+json":{"type":"string"}},"metadata":{},"execution_count":11}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["def tentukan_pemenang(pemain, komputer):\n","    if pemain == komputer:\n","        return \"Seri!\"\n","    elif (pemain == \"gunting\" and komputer == \"kertas\") or \\\n","         (pemain == \"batu\" and komputer == \"gunting\") or \\\n","         (pemain == \"kertas\" and komputer == \"batu\"):\n","        return \"Kamu menang!\"\n","    else:\n","        return \"Komputer menang!\"\n","\n","while True:\n","    pilihan_pemain = input('Pilih antara batu, gunting, atau kertas : ')\n","    pilihan_komputer = random.choice(['batu', 'gunting', 'kertas'])\n","\n","    print(\"Pemain memilih : \", pilihan_pemain)\n","    print(\"Komputer memilih : \", pilihan_komputer)\n","\n","    if pilihan_pemain.lower() in ['batu', 'gunting', 'kertas']:\n","        print(tentukan_pemenang(pilihan_pemain, pilihan_komputer))\n","    else:\n","        print('Pilihan tidak valid')\n","\n","    main_lagi = input(\"Masukkan 'y' untuk bermain lagi : \").lower()\n","\n","    if main_lagi != 'y':\n","        print('Terima kasih sudah bermain')\n","        break\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"Q_sCjbHXr-K9","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1744624694821,"user_tz":-420,"elapsed":63680,"user":{"displayName":"Elmo Allistair","userId":"10987414782066235031"}},"outputId":"fa8c924f-064f-4a8e-ac1d-6a03ad759881"},"execution_count":14,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Pilih antara batu, gunting, atau kertas : kertas\n","Pemain memilih :  kertas\n","Komputer memilih :  gunting\n","Komputer menang!\n","Masukkan 'y' untuk bermain lagi : y\n","Pilih antara batu, gunting, atau kertas : pistol\n","Pemain memilih :  pistol\n","Komputer memilih :  batu\n","Pilihan tidak valid\n","Masukkan 'y' untuk bermain lagi : tidak\n","Terima kasih sudah bermain\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"9kWi7wNCjJ78"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]}],"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyMVW1k0KsI4opJYGZjm014q"},"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0}